message.body: I wasnt planning since we didnt touch base. So prob more like 5 or 5:30. I told kate i'd grab a beverage with her. Wanna come?
Cool, whats your address? Colin is in for tonight. And where should i meet yal for a beverage?
We made it ti skinny. See you

Hey brother! Good morning. Could you pass on colin's number? Lets plan next time to get as trees dance going, and also lets have something worked up for that tune/rhythm of yours. Molly really liked what you were doing with it. Shoot me any melodies in paper or audio. Peace!
